### Author : Ghita TAZI

CHALLENGE
------------

The goal is to consume a Web Service that publishes the CAC40 and NASDAQ rates<br />
The app must:<br />
- show the retrieved values on a table and a graph<br />
- make the table cells editable: when the user modifies a cells, the update is also shown on the graph<br />
- refresh the values every second and update table and graph, keeping the user eventual modifications<br />
The graph should be drawn using D3js<br />

INSTALLATION
------------

Install node.js<br />
At the project's root, execute: npm install<br />

BUILD
-----

Execute: npm start<br />
In the address bar of your favorite browser, type: 127.0.0.1:8000<br />